    <div class="prose">
      <div class="te-block">
        <p>Colorectal cancer India లో rapidly increasing cancer. Urban dietary patterns, sedentary lifestyle, late presentation common factors.</p>
        <p>Rectal cancer కి TME (Total Mesorectal Excision) gold standard. Richard Heald దీన్ని develop చేశారు. Dutch TME Trial ఇది local recurrence dramatically తగ్గిస్తుందని prove చేసింది. నేను ఈ technique follow చేస్తాను.</p>
        <p>Laparoscopic colon resection oncological outcomes open surgery కి equivalent అని multiple RCTs confirm చేశాయి. Smaller incisions, faster recovery, earlier adjuvant therapy start. నేను suitable cases లో routinely laparoscopic approach use చేస్తాను.</p>
        <p>Colorectal cancer peritoneum కి spread అయిన selected cases లో, PRODIGE 7 trial HIPEC benefit show చేసింది. PCI score, overall disease burden బట్టి consider చేస్తాను.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="en-block">
        <p>Colorectal cancer is rapidly rising in India, driven by urban dietary patterns, sedentary lifestyle and late presentation.</p>
        <p>For rectal cancer, TME (Total Mesorectal Excision) is the gold standard, developed by Richard Heald. The Dutch TME Trial proved it dramatically reduces local recurrence. I follow this technique.</p>
        <p>Multiple RCTs have confirmed that laparoscopic colon resection gives oncological outcomes equivalent to open surgery. Smaller incisions, faster recovery and earlier start of adjuvant therapy. I routinely use the laparoscopic approach in suitable cases.</p>
        <p>For selected colorectal cancer cases with peritoneal spread, the PRODIGE 7 trial showed HIPEC benefit. I consider it based on PCI score and overall disease burden.</p>
